sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CM as Conversation Manager
    participant Router as Intent Router
    participant AgentA as Query Agent
    participant AgentB as Job Agent
    participant LLM
    participant Tools
    participant State as State Store
    
    User->>CM: "Find expensive queries in job 123"
    
    Note over CM: Complex request spans<br/>multiple domains
    
    CM->>Router: classify_intent()
    Router->>LLM: "Classify user intent"
    LLM-->>Router: { primary: "job", secondary: "query" }
    Router-->>CM: Start with JobAgent
    
    CM->>AgentA: create_agent(JobAgent)
    CM->>State: Create SharedContext
    State-->>CM: Context ID
    
    Note over AgentA: Process job analysis
    AgentA->>Tools: resolve_job(123)
    Tools-->>AgentA: Job Metadata
    
    AgentA->>Tools: get_job_tasks(123)
    Tools-->>AgentA: Task List
    
    Note over AgentA: Identifies query<br/>optimization needed
    
    AgentA->>CM: request_handoff(QueryAgent, context)
    
    Note over CM: Preserve context<br/>for handoff
    CM->>State: Update SharedContext<br/>{ job_id: 123, tasks: [...] }
    State-->>CM: ✓ Updated
    
    CM->>AgentA: finalize_output()
    AgentA-->>CM: Partial Output
    
    CM->>AgentB: create_agent(QueryAgent)
    CM->>State: Load SharedContext
    State-->>CM: { job_id: 123, tasks: [...] }
    
    CM->>AgentB: process_with_context(message, context)
    
    Note over AgentB: Continue from where<br/>JobAgent left off
    
    AgentB->>Tools: resolve_query(statement_ids)
    Tools-->>AgentB: Query Details
    
    AgentB->>Tools: analyze_query_plan()
    Tools-->>AgentB: Performance Issues
    
    AgentB->>LLM: "Generate optimization recommendations"
    LLM-->>AgentB: Recommendations
    
    AgentB-->>CM: FinalOutputEvent
    
    CM->>CM: merge_outputs(JobAgent, QueryAgent)
    
    CM->>State: Persist Full Conversation
    Note over State: Stores agent transitions<br/>and shared context
    
    CM-->>User: Combined Output<br/>(Job + Query Analysis)
    
    Note over User: Seamless experience<br/>despite agent handoff

